]], [[Ireland]]<br />Outdoor<br />Grass<br />[[South of Ireland Championships|Singles]]  ||{{flagicon|Ireland|1783}} Edward Montiford Longfield Lysaght<br />7-5 6-4 6-0 ||{{flagicon|Ireland|1783}} William H. Gavin|| rowspan=2| {{flagicon|GBR}} Captain Frederick Thomas Verschoyle<br />6-3 6-3 6-3<br /> {{flagicon|GBR}} Edmond Bennet Brackenbury<br /> walkover|| rowspan=2| {{flagicon|Ireland|1783}} William Dawson<br />6-1 6-3 6-3 <br />{{flagicon|ENG}} Major Henry Holley Goodeve<br />6-3 6-3 6-3 <br />{{flagicon|ENG}} Chaloner Knox<br />walkover<br />{{flagicon|Ireland|1783}} R.D. O'Brien<br />6-3 6-3 6-3\n|-valign=top\n| ||\n|-valign=top\n|rowspan=2| 2\u20135 August||rowspan=2|[[Darlington Tournament]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Darlington 1882|url=http://www.tennisarchives.com/voorloopfiche.php?wedstrijdvoorloopid=4548|website=tennisarchives.com|publisher=Tennis Archives|accessdate=29 October 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"lawn_tennis_calendar\" /> <br /> [[Darlington]], [[Great Britain]]<br />Outdoor<br />Grass<br />[[1882 Darlington Tournament|Singles]] ||{{flagicon|ENG}} Arthur Wellesley Hallward<br />6-1 4-6 6-1 6-3|| {{flagicon|NZ}} Minden Fenwick <br />|| rowspan=2| {{flagicon|Ireland|1783}} Sir William Henry Mahon <br />6-3 4-6 6-5 0-6 6-5<br /> {{flagicon|NZ}} Mark Fenwick <br />6-4 6-1 6-4|| rowspan=2| {{flagicon|NZ}} Minden Fenwick <br />Bye<br />{{flagicon|NZ}} Percival Clennell Fenwick <br />6-5 3-6 6-4 1-6 6-4<br />{{flagicon|ENG}} Richard Paul Agar Swettenham <br />6-2 6-1 6-1 <br />{{flagicon|GBR}} H. Mason <br />4-6 6-0 6-2 6-2\n|-valign=top\n| ||\n|-valign=top\n|rowspan=2| 7\u201312 August||rowspan=2|[[Waterford Annual Lawn Tennis Tournament]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Waterford 1882|url=http://www.tennisarchives.com/voorloopfiche.php?wedstrijdvoorloopid=6245|website=tennisarchives.com|publisher=Tennis Archives|accessdate=29 October 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Evelegh|first1=B.C.|title=Lawn Tennis Calendar|journal=The Field|date=1882}}</ref> <br /> Waterfor